Setup Instructions
First, install dependencies:
1. npm list express
2. npm install express express-session
3. npm init -y
Check if express-session is installed locally:
npm list express-session
1. Visit http://localhost:3000/login â†’ Session created
2. Visit http://localhost:3000/profile â†’ Shows username
3. Visit http://localhost:3000/logout â†’ Session destroyed
